    document.getElementById('map-text').innerHTML = '<p>When the surprise attack began, dozens of terrorists infiltrated the southern city. They fired in all directions, murdering civilians they encountered in the street. This was at the same time as incessant rocket fire towards the city and the other communities in the envelope. At an early hour, the terrorists stormed the Sderot police station. The policemen tried to fend off the terrorists bravely, but many fell in battle. 7 of them, station policemen. After 25 hours of heavy fighting, it was not until 4 a.m. on Sunday morning that control of the station was achieved.\nFive days after the battle, which led to the complete destruction of the building, a new temporary station was inaugurated in the city.</p>';
